Question: Shenzhen Hudson Technology co., ltd. CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Huntkey

Product Highlights at CES 2024

- F45 Slim GaN fast charger with 2 USB-C ports, foldable pins, and 45W maximum output
- Desktop charging stations for office and home use with 10 circuit protections and support for 35W, 68W, and 100W GaN fast charging
- PC PSU MVP P1200 with 1200W power, Intel ATX3.0 standard compliance, 80 Plus platinum certification, and 60s delayed cooling
- Industrial standard ATX power supplies with side fan and double ball design, support for PCIE5.0 graphics card interface, and 80 PLUS gold medal energy efficiency
- Exhibition Date: 9-12 January
- Address: Las Vegas
- Booth: Westgate Hall, 2421
- Website: https://www.huntkey.com
